    <h4>Sizes</h2>
    <p>Large and Small are the two sticky banner sizes. The large size spans the full-width of the browser window and therefore can’t have rounded corners. The small size is fixed width and features rounded corners on top. The large size can feature more

    than the small size as well, including a thumbnail image, more text, and a larger call to action.</p>



