    <h4 id="content">Content</h4>
    <p>Content in the large size falls within the 12-column grid whereas content in the small size is determined by the width of the banner container.</p>

    <h4>Call to action</h4>
    <p>The large sticky banner features a Primary call to action and the small sticky banner features a Default call to action. The large size should have a Primary call to action, even if the same style is present somewhere else on the page. The banner is shown after a user has scrolled past the hero to avoid displaying two Primary calls to action simultaneously.</p>

